articles.title: Badminton Asia Championships: Satwik-Chirag pair ensures men's doubles medal after 52 years - Times of India
articles.description: Badminton News: India's top men's doubles pair Satwiksairaj Rankireddy and Chirag Shetty scripted history by assuring a men's doubles medal at the Badminton Asia Cham
